The paper presents a framework that uses a CNN-based structure for stock market prediction. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also involves the use of historical data and the extraction of common patterns, which suggests that it may also belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Computational Economics (cs.CE) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of a CNN-based structure suggests that the paper may also belong to the Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) sub-category.
